snippet.title: Malware - PC Gameplay
snippet.description:
About The Game

You travel back in time and space to 1999, a pastoral era that once belonged to the Internet. However, you find that this era is not as beautiful as you remember. Rogue software, malicious installations, these Internet dregs that should belong to the future have already occupied the Internet world at this time. 

Title: Malware
Developer: Odd Games
Publisher: Odd Games
Release Date: 1 Aug, 2024
Genre: Casual, Simulation, Puzzle, Strategy, Point & Click, Hidden Object, Text-Based
